number of guests? numberOfGuests (used to calculate prices of other items)
what food is being served? (speghetti -- chicken something -- steak)
beverages? water/soda/coffee -- beer/wine -- open bar
music? dj -- live music
entertainment? clowns/face painting -- comedy performance
giveaways

to create simplicity I have added option numbers instead of asking the user to type out whole strings of words that would have to match up exactly


other options:


